from.S: report.delivered_new_pk n left join report.delivered_combined_hist e on n.orggame = e.orggame

select.S: n.orggame, n.game_reference, n.most_recent_file, n.game_id, n.org, n.delivered, n.last_modified, n.game_date, n.level, getdate() as date_processed

where.S: n.game_date like '2019%' and e.orggame is null
